# Placeholder for assets directory

Add the following image files to this directory:
- icon.png (1024x1024) - App icon
- splash.png (1284x2778) - Splash screen
- adaptive-icon.png (1024x1024) - Android adaptive icon
- favicon.png (48x48) - Web favicon

You can use any image editor to create these, or use placeholder images.
The app will work without them in Expo Go, but they're needed for production builds.
